track_notes: Arrive at road/trail start via Alta Rd. and Juvenile Detention Facility entrance road. This steep trail is accessible via high clearance 4WD--you will need 4 Lo. I drove half (Jeep Wrangler Rubicon) and walked the rest of the way to summit via road and use trails.
This is another route up the hill.  A bit over one mile and almost 1,000 ft of elevation gain.
